This private diligence package includes first-party ShadowProof Bridge source code,
documentation, schemas, tests, and local simulation assets. The package declares an
external dependency on jsonschema for schema validation and optional production/dev
dependencies listed in pyproject.toml. Lean, Mathlib, frontier model providers,
Redis, Postgres, OpenTelemetry, Uvicorn, and MCP SDK assets are integration targets
or optional dependencies and are not bundled as vendored third-party source in this
archive.

Recipients should run their own legal, open-source, export-control, security, and
model-governance review before production use or acquisition close.
